{"tid":2245422,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"銀湖。天峰 兇宅同層戶劈310萬沽","createTime":"2020-10-16T08:10:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T11:56:29.000Z","uid":345221,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"4aafe3754c56dd81dba7fd48a943974f4bd16a37","tid":2245422,"uid":345221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T08:10:47.000Z","msg":"【信報財經新聞】馬鞍山銀湖．天峰8座中低層B室，實用面積約762方呎，建築面積約1005方呎，3房套房連儲物房間隔，外望清幽山景，今年7月中放售，原業主開價1250萬元，終以940萬元以交吉形式成功沽出，劈價達310萬元，實用呎價約12336元，建築呎價約9353元。<br />\n<br />\n利嘉閣地產表示，原業主於2009年6月以約502.8萬元購入上述單位，持貨至今約11年，現轉手賬面獲利約437.2萬元，物業升值約87%。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，上述單位市場價格約1240萬元，但同層有凶宅單位，故上述成交價較市場價格低約300萬元或約24%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://finance.now.com/news/post.php?isapp=1&amp;id=616663\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffinance.now.com%2Fnews%2Fpost.php%3Fisapp%3D1%26id%3D616663&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVU6zbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=fcd2181a\" target=\"_blank\">https://finance.now.com/news/post.php?isapp=1&amp;id=616663</a>"},{"pid":"e446ee2cb1a25170bd89970b29e830de4908e01f","tid":2245422,"uid":19712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T08:12:05.000Z","msg":"凶宅係咪難小小申請按揭?"},{"pid":"a7cb5bfcccef62363abf56ca56b7db98998d9b9e","tid":2245422,"uid":337986,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T08:12:46.000Z","msg":"馬鞍山 有一千萬洗撚買呢度咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9acd7d49569361dd198c0abbe2f9ef7fcf1e332","tid":2245422,"uid":345221,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"e446ee2cb1a25170bd89970b29e830de4908e01f","tid":2245422,"uid":19712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T08:12:05.000Z","msg":"凶宅係咪難小小申請按揭?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T08:13:09.000Z","msg":"呢個係兇宅同層 唔知有無影響"},{"pid":"b7a8a4edddce829984cc7c555f3e3989f2a001e9","tid":2245422,"uid":345221,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"a7cb5bfcccef62363abf56ca56b7db98998d9b9e","tid":2245422,"uid":337986,"